ss='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-17\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/lam-the-nao-de-co-the-chup-anh-ngoai-canh-dep.html\/#Quy_trinh_thuc_hien_dich_vu_chup_anh_ngoai_canh_cua_chung_toi_bao_gom\" title=\"Quy tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bao g\u1ed3m:\">Quy tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bao g\u1ed3m:<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-18\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/lam-the-nao-de-co-the-chup-anh-ngoai-canh-dep.html\/#Cam_ket_cua_chung_toi_khi_ki_ket_su_dung_dich_vu_chup_anh_ngoai_canh_tai_Achaumedia\" title=\"Cam k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i khi k\u00ed k\u1ebft s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh t\u1ea1i Achaumedia:\u00a0\">Cam k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i khi k\u00ed k\u1ebft s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh t\u1ea1i Achaumedia:\u00a0<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>Trong m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i ch\u01a1i, vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn khung c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn cho m\u00ecnh nh\u1eefng shot h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eb9p l\u01b0u gi\u1eef k\u1ec9 ni\u1ec7m l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. V\u1eady mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m h\u00ecnh\u00a0<em><strong>ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p<\/strong><\/em>, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u01b0u \u00fd nh\u1eefng tips g\u00ec? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1edbi <a href=\"http:\/\/achaumedia.vn\"><strong>Achaumedia<\/strong><\/a> \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam nh\u00e9.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chup_anh_ngoai_canh_la_gi\"><\/span><strong>Ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh ch\u1ee5p \u1edf ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 b\u1eaft m\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u00e1nh m\u1eaft t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i, vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee5p nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m h\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi \u00e1nh n\u1eafng thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean c\u00f9ng trang ph\u1ee5c tr\u1eafng tr\u1ebbo, tinh kh\u00f4i b\u1eaft m\u1eaft ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho nh\u1eefng t\u00edn \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111am m\u00ea ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nhung_luu_y_khi_chup_anh_ngoai_canh_de_co_nhung_tam_hinh_dep_la_gi\"><\/span><strong>Nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd khi ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eb9p l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Thoi_diem_chup_anh\"><\/span><strong>1. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh:<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh theo m\u00ecnh th\u1ea5y l\u00e0 t\u1eeb 6h s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ebfn 10h s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 chi\u1ec1u l\u00e0 t\u1eeb sau 16 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1ed1i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian n\u1eafng v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb n\u00f3ng v\u00e0 g\u1eaft do \u00e1nh n\u1eafng. H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf l\u00fac gi\u1eefa tr\u01b0a v\u00ec khi ch\u1ee5p gi\u1edd n\u00e0y \u00e1nh n\u1eafng s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfu v\u00e0o m\u1eaft l\u00e0m c\u00f4 d\u00e2u ch\u00fa r\u1ec3 nheo m\u1eaft c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 d\u1ec5 ra m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i s\u1ebd b\u1ecb b\u00f3ng da m\u1eb7t. Khi tr\u1eddi n\u1eafng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf ch\u1ee5p theo chi\u1ec1u n\u1eafng v\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 da m\u1eb7t m\u1eabu s\u1ebd b\u1ecb b\u00f3ng hay \u00e1m m\u00e0u n\u1eafng, n\u1ebfu ch\u1ee5p theo chi\u1ec1u n\u1eafng c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n n\u00ean d\u00f9ng t\u1ea5m che m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi nh\u1eb1m h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u00e1nh n\u1eafng g\u1eaft, ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm b\u00f3ng c\u00e2y m\u00e1t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee5p, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u00e1nh n\u1eafng loang l\u1ed5 chi\u1ebfu v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t m\u1eabu. N\u1ebfu ch\u1ee5p ng\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eafng th\u00ec n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1eaft s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e8n flash \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh v\u00e0o v\u00f9ng t\u1ed1i. Nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ee5p\u00a0File Raw\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda h\u1eadu k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb9p h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14093 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1258\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh1.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh1-300x184.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh1-1024x629.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh1-768x472.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh1-1536x944.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Lua_chon_trang_phuc_phu_hop\"><\/span><strong>2. L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn trang ph\u1ee5c ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>T\u00f9y v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn cho m\u1eabu trang ph\u1ee5c ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh, t\u00f9y v\u00e0o m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0u s\u1eafc kh\u00e1c nhau \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0u trang ph\u1ee5c ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. M\u00ecnh l\u1ea5y v\u00ed d\u1ee5 n\u1ebfu c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ch\u1ee5p ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh \u1edf nh\u1eefng n\u01a1i nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e2y xanh nhi\u1ec1u hoa\u2026 t\u01b0\u01a1i t\u1eafn th\u00ec n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn trang ph\u1ee5c nh\u00ed nh\u1ea3nh m\u00e0u t\u01b0\u01a1i x\u00edu nh\u1eb1m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi khung h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi h\u1eadu k\u1ef3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\u00a0Blend m\u00e0u trong tr\u1ebbo. Hay khi ch\u1ee5p \u1edf nh\u1eefng n\u01a1i m\u00e0u tr\u1ea7m nh\u01b0 ch\u00f9a chi\u1ec1n,nh\u00e0 c\u1ed5\u2026 th\u00ec c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 trang ph\u1ee5c t\u1ed1i m\u00e0u ch\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 \u0103n nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi quang c\u1ea3nh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady h\u00ecnh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi h\u01a1n , khi ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda h\u1eadu k\u1ef3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 blend m\u00e0u vintage hay m\u00e0u h\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c\u2026<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14092 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"912\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh.jpg 1280w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh-300x214.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh-1024x730.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh-768x547.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Style_list_huong_dan_cach_tao_dang_cho_mau\"><\/span><strong>3. Style list h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng cho m\u1eabu<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi khi ch\u1ee5p s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eabu \u0111i ch\u1ee5p l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e0nh ra s\u1ebd kh\u00e1 l\u00fang t\u00fang v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3n n\u00e0y, v\u00ec th\u1ebf c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n n\u00ean t\u1ea1o cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t b\u00ed k\u00edp b\u1ed9 s\u01b0u t\u1ea7m c\u00e1c c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng ri\u00eang, n\u1ebfu ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem\u00a0C\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng khi ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh nh\u00e9. Tuy nhi\u00ean t\u00f9y v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea3nh m\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00a0t\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i hay t\u00f9y bi\u1ebfn ra c\u00e1c ki\u1ec3u t\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng kh\u00e1c nhau cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t m\u1eabu hay \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ee5p.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14096 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"828\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh4.jpg 1280w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh4-300x194.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh4-1024x662.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh4-768x497.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Xac_dinh_la_di_chup_lay_canh_hay_la_chup_xoa_phong\"><\/span><strong>4. X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 \u0111i ch\u1ee5p l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3nh hay l\u00e0 ch\u1ee5p x\u00f3a ph\u00f4ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n, m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh th\u1ea5y l\u00e0 \u0111a s\u1ed1 khi ch\u1ee5p ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh x\u00f3a ph\u00f4ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u1ed1ng k\u00ednh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. N\u1ebfu x\u00f3a ph\u00f4ng th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng 85F\/1.8 hay 70-200F\/4 hay F\/2.8 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 50F\/1.8. Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee5p l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3nh th\u00ec c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n kh\u00e9p kh\u1ea9u l\u1ea1i ho\u1eb7c d\u00f9ng lens g\u00f3c r\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 35F2 hay 24F\/2.8\u2026.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14098 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1307\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh6.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh6-300x191.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh6-1024x654.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh6-768x490.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh6-1536x980.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5_Xu_ly_hau_ky\"><\/span><strong>5. X\u1eed l\u00fd h\u1eadu k\u1ef3<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>T\u00f9y v\u00e0o \u1ea3nh c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ed7i hay kh\u00f4ng hay mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda cho m\u00e0u t\u01b0\u01a1i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u00e0u bu\u1ed3n kh\u00e1c nhau c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng photoshop c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 lightroom \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda \u1ea3nh c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14099 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1258\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh8.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh8-300x184.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh8-1024x629.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh8-768x472.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh8-1536x944.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam:\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-chup-anh-san-pham-do-thu-cong-my-nghe.html\/\"><em><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ed3 th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng m\u1ef9 ngh\u1ec7<\/strong><\/em><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nhung_cach_tao_dang_chup_anh_ngoai_canh_dep_ma_ban_can_biet\"><\/span><strong>Nh\u1eefng c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft!<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Quay_lung_ve_Camera\"><\/span><strong>1. Quay l\u01b0ng v\u1ec1 Camera:\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>N\u00ean ch\u1ee5p c\u1eadn c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4n l\u00ean v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p tr\u00ean \u0111\u00f4i vai c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Ki\u1ec3u n\u00e0y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee5p m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 n\u01a1i \u0111\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00ec c\u00e0ng h\u1ee3p. Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eabu hay di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean tr\u00ean th\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eady, c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00eda sau th\u00ec ki\u1ec3u ch\u1ee5p n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng t\u00f4n th\u00eam gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb cho b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14103 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh11.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1377\" height=\"2048\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh11.jpg 1377w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh11-202x300.jpg 202w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh11-689x1024.jpg 689w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh11-768x1142.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh11-1033x1536.jpg 1033w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1377px) 100vw, 1377px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Mot_tay_ven_toc\"><\/span><strong>2. M\u1ed9t tay v\u00e9n t\u00f3c:<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>T\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t b\u1edd t\u01b0\u1eddng hoa hay h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o, c\u1ed5ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat \u00e1nh n\u1eafng \u0111\u1ed5 b\u00f3ng c\u00e2y xu\u1ed1ng l\u00e0 c\u00f3 ngay m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m \u1ea3nh m\u1ed9ng m\u01a1.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Chan_duoi_chan_co\"><\/span><strong>3. Ch\u00e2n du\u1ed7i ch\u00e2n co:<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00f4 n\u00e0ng c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u c\u00e0ng khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n, nh\u1ecf nh\u1eafn xinh x\u1eafn nh\u01b0 c\u00e2y n\u1ea5m. C\u00e1ch ch\u1ee5p n\u00e0y gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n \u0103n gian th\u00eam chi\u1ec1u cao kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u.<\/p>\n<p>M\u1eb9o: N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean ch\u1ee5p nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5m \u1ea3nh qu\u00e1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1eadn ra khuy\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1eafm. Khi \u0111\u1ee9ng ch\u1ee5p th\u1eed \u0111\u01b0a camera th\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t t\u00ed, b\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n l\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi cao h\u01a1n b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh th\u00ec \u0111\u1ee9ng l\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ecd kho\u1ea3ng 1 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n l\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o 2 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nhau, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1eb9o nh\u1ecf v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3m quan h\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc m\u00e0 c\u00e1c th\u1ee3 ch\u1ee5p hay ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 hay \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng trong c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng gian c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Tay_che_mat_troi\"><\/span><strong>4. Tay che m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi:<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 che ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u01b0a tay v\u00e9n t\u00f3c c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t th\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng n\u1eefa. N\u00ean ch\u1ee5p v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i b\u00ecnh minh v\u00e0 ho\u00e0ng h\u00f4n.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14104 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1365\" height=\"2048\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh12.jpg 1365w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh12-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh12-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh12-768x1152.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh12-1024x1536.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1365px) 100vw, 1365px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5_Gio_thoi_bay_toc\"><\/span><strong>5. Gi\u00f3 th\u1ed5i bay t\u00f3c:<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ki\u1ec3u ch\u1ee5p kh\u00e1c. kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 gi\u00f3 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o ho\u1eb7c v\u1eeba b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i v\u1eeba quay \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"6_Tua_lung_len_ghe_tao_dang_sang_chanh\"><\/span><strong>6. T\u1ef1a l\u01b0ng l\u00ean gh\u1ebf, t\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng sang ch\u1ea3nh:<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Ng\u1ed3i t\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng g\u00e1c m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n l\u00ean \u0111\u00f9i, tay v\u00e9n t\u00f3c t\u1ea1o t\u1ea1o n\u00ean v\u1ebb qu\u00fd ph\u00e1i sang tr\u1ecdng n\u1ebfu kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi 1 kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p. T\u01b0 th\u1ebf ch\u1ee5p n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ki\u1ec3u ch\u1ee5p quay l\u01b0ng v\u1ec1 camera, d\u00f9ng kinh m\u1eaft hay che \u1ea3nh m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 combo ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh sang ch\u1ea3nh gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 tin khoe nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh du l\u1ecbch \u0111\u1eb9p l\u00ean instagram r\u1ed3i.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14102 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1454\" height=\"2048\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh10.jpg 1454w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh10-213x300.jpg 213w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh10-727x1024.jpg 727w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh10-768x1082.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh10-1091x1536.jpg 1091w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1454px) 100vw, 1454px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"7_Tan_dung_anh_sang_tu_nhien\"><\/span><strong>7. T\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean: <\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n khi mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eb9p l\u00e0 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng trong h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb9p. \u00c1nh s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1eb9p gi\u00fap b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n, c\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft r\u00f5 n\u00e9t v\u00e0 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 h\u01a1n. \u00c1nh s\u00e1ng chu\u1ea9n cho nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p l\u00e0 t\u1ea7m 3 \u2013 5 gi\u1edd chi\u1ec1u \u2013 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 ch\u00f3i nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 cho t\u1eebng khung h\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14100 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1296\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh7.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh7-300x190.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh7-1024x648.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh7-768x486.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chup_anh_ngoai_canh7-1536x972.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam:\u00a0<em><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-chup-anh-san-pham-do-thu-cong-my-nghe.html\/\">D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh doanh nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ea1i khu v\u1ef1c mi\u1ec1n B\u1eafc<\/a><\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-image\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Achaumedia_ho_tro_dich_vu_chup_anh_ngoai_canh_dep_nhat_danh_cho_ban\"><\/span><strong>Achaumedia h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t d\u00e0nh cho b\u1ea1n:<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quy_trinh_thuc_hien_dich_vu_chup_anh_ngoai_canh_cua_chung_toi_bao_gom\"><\/span><strong>Quy tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bao g\u1ed3m:<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: Nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin s\u1eed dung d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>B\u1ea1n li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean CSKH s\u1ebd t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n b\u00e1o gi\u00e1, ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng t\u1eeb b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: L\u00ean \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ho\u1eb7c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n l\u00ean \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng. Sau qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh trao \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: Th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<p>H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e9t, \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e1ng \u2026 sao cho \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi giao s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. Giao tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng xem x\u00e9t v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda.<\/p>\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: Ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 giao s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh, nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n file ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n cho qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cam_ket_cua_chung_toi_khi_ki_ket_su_dung_dich_vu_chup_anh_ngoai_canh_tai_Achaumedia\"><\/span><strong>Cam k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i khi k\u00ed k\u1ebft s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh t\u1ea1i Achaumedia:\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p:<\/strong>\u00a0C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 vi\u00ean nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh, m\u1ecdi th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi, gi\u00fap ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng project \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00fang h\u1ea1n, \u0111\u00fang th\u1eddi gian nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Trang thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i:<\/strong>\u00a0Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb, c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3, di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u1edbc phim ch\u00e2n th\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 c\u1ea1nh tranh, h\u1ee3p l\u00fd:<\/strong>\u00a0T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 chi ph\u00ed d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f4ng khai, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o l\u00e0 r\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111a s\u1ed1 doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<li><strong>\u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o nh\u1eefng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t d\u00e0nh cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng:<\/strong>\u00a0Khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t d\u00e0nh cho b\u1ea1n khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n vi\u1ec7c k\u00ed k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hai b\u00ean lu\u00f4n t\u1ef1 nguy\u1ec7n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng deadline th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c nhanh ch\u00f3ng nh\u1ea5t c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea3m s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9 tin c\u1eady, uy t\u00edn nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Lu\u00f4n l\u1eafng nghe, lu\u00f4n th\u1ea5u hi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c.<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Nh\u1eefng cam k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p:\u00a0<\/strong>Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn ekip l\u00e0m phim l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong ngh\u1ec1. M\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng hay s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 x\u1ea3y ra trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng hy h\u1eefu \u00edt c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. H\u1ecd lu\u00f4n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n quay phim ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00fat ng\u1eafn v\u00e0 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Trang thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i:<\/strong>\u00a0H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng m\u00e1y quay phim \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cam k\u1ebft l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i m\u00e1y t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh r\u00f5 n\u00e9t nh\u1ea5t ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0: m\u00e1y GoPro HERO3 Black Edition, Canon Vixia HF G30,\u2026\u0111\u1ec3 cho ra nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u1edbc phim ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o nh\u1ea5t.<\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bao-gia-san-xuat-video-clip.html\/\"><strong>Gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 h\u1ee3p l\u00ed:<\/strong><\/a>\u00a0\u0110\u1eb9p \u2013 \u0111\u1ed9c nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m \u1edf m\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 l\u00e0m phim. M\u1ed7i doanh nghi\u1ec7p khi \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 l\u00e0m phim c\u1ee7a\u00a0<strong>\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/strong>\u00a0\u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ty.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u01b0u \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5m h\u00ecnh\u00a0<em><strong>ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p.\u00a0<\/strong><\/em>N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/quay-phim-chup-anh\/\"><strong>d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh<\/strong><\/a> c\u1ee7a Achaumedia, h\u00e3y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Trong m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i ch\u01a1i, vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn khung c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn cho m\u00ecnh nh\u1eefng shot h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eb9p l\u01b0u gi\u1eef k\u1ec9 ni\u1ec7m l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. V\u1eady mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m h\u00ecnh\u00a0ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u01b0u \u00fd nh\u1eefng tips g\u00ec? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1edbi Achaumedia \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":13896,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[813,63],"tags":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v18.7 (Yoast SEO v19.9) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>L\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n?<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"V\u1eady mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m h\u00ecnh\u00a0ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u01b0u \u00fd nh\u1eefng tips g\u00ec? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1edbi Achaumedia \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam nh\u00e9.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/lam-the-nao-de-co-the-chup-anh-ngoai-canh-dep.html\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"vi_VN\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"L\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p?\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"V\u1eady mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m h\u00ecnh\u00a0ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u01b0u \u00fd nh\u1eefng tips g\u00ec? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v